```http
### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api

### ============================================
### ENDPOINTS GENERALES
### ============================================

### GET - Inicio del servidor
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### GET - Información de la API
GET {{apiUrl}}

### ============================================
### ENDPOINTS CERVEZA - /api/birra
### ============================================

### GET - Obtener página de cerveza
GET {{apiUrl}}/birra
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET - Obtener todas las cervezas
GET {{apiUrl}}/birra/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET - Obtener cerveza por ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/birra/699ca391d278124389f43e06
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST - Crear nueva cerveza
POST {{apiUrl}}/birra
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Cerveza Premium",
  "precio": 2.5
}

### PUT - Actualizar cerveza
PUT {{apiUrl}}/birra/69a730128df0bfbff5deb1b3
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "nombre": "Cerveza Premium Actualizada",
  "precio": 3.0
}

### DELETE - Eliminar cerveza
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/birra/69a7300c8df0bfbff5deb1b0
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### ENDPOINTS VINO - /api/vinito
### ============================================

### GET - Obtener página de vino
GET {{apiUrl}}/vinito
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET - Obtener todos los vinos
GET {{apiUrl}}/vinito/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### GET - Obtener vino por ID
GET {{apiUrl}}/vinito/699caacdd3ab04d4f6c8f4ca
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### POST - Crear nuevo vino
POST {{apiUrl}}/vinito
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Vino Tinto Reserva",
  "descripcion": "Vino tinto de alta calidad, con notas de frutas rojas y un toque de roble"
}

### PUT - Actualizar vino
PUT {{apiUrl}}/vinito/69a730ea9dcea9707f5b1206
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Vino Blanco Actualizado",
  "descripcion": "Vino blanco fresco y afrutado, perfecto para maridar con pescados y mariscos"
}

### DELETE - Eliminar vino
DELETE {{apiUrl}}/vinito/69a730ea9dcea9707f5b1206
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### AUTENTICACIÓN - /api/auth
### ============================================

@token =  eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpZCI6IjY5YTcyZTU3ZTYxNWZmMWY5NzEzMTgyNSIsImlhdCI6MTc3MjU2NDQ1MSwiZXhwIjoxNzczMTY5MjUxfQ.7EWCXyeNbdGkXc0m__HRNfngz7hRUjPrv03ppspYhRw

### POST - Registro de usuario (crear cuenta)
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/registro
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ciro@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### POST - Login (obtiene JWT)
POST {{apiUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ciro@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### INSTRUCCIONES:
# 1) Ejecuta la petición de Login y copia el valor de `token` del JSON de respuesta.
# 2) Pega el token arriba en la variable `@token` (reemplaza el valor vacío).

### GET - Obtener perfil (ruta protegida) — necesita header Authorization
GET {{apiUrl}}/auth/perfil
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### PUT - Actualizar perfil (ruta protegida) — requiere Authorization
PUT {{apiUrl}}/auth/perfil
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "email": "frankakakakaka@example.com",
  "password": "nuevaPass456"
}

